    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique can only be used on a target that is a size category no larger than yours, which you must currently be in a grapple with. Make an opposed grapple check against the target. If it hits, you slam the opponent into the ground, dealing your unarmed attack damage, plus 1 per Strength and Speed Rank you are currently benefiting from (maximum +5). In addition, the target is @Condition[staggered;duration=2]{staggered} for two rounds (Fortitude negates).<br><br>The target is left @Condition[prone]{prone} after this technique hits, but both you and the target will no longer be grappled.</p>\n\n<hr><p><b>Empower:</b> Spend 1 Chakra to increase the damage by 1d6, up to 4d6 bonus damage.</p>\n\n",
